{"tid":1112660,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"馬國明算唔算係夏商周三代以來第一完人?","createTime":"2019-04-17T13:36:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-17T14:09:44.000Z","uid":76115,"like":10,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"98231165ebaad883bced72954753680230139fcf","tid":1112660,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T13:36:23.000Z","msg":"馬國明係一個好好嘅人"},{"pid":"08bb73cb62f16a1b2f592a28efdba7018054eedd","tid":1112660,"uid":112211,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"98231165ebaad883bced72954753680230139fcf","tid":1112660,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T13:36:23.000Z","msg":"馬國明係一個好好嘅人"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T13:37:13.000Z","msg":"馬明係一個冇壞既人"},{"pid":"f0c306b32b3f4b180fa806e64aaed2f3fe4b7e71","tid":1112660,"uid":88491,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"08bb73cb62f16a1b2f592a28efdba7018054eedd","tid":1112660,"uid":112211,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"98231165ebaad883bced72954753680230139fcf","tid":1112660,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T13:36:23.000Z","msg":"馬國明係一個好好嘅人"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T13:37:13.000Z","msg":"馬明係一個冇壞既人"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T13:38:25.000Z","msg":"馬明係一個有靈魂嘅人"},{"pid":"8f63c22a9ce1735fcd35ac1b128f0375475b8979","tid":1112660,"uid":182930,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T13:45:17.000Z","msg":"強烈要求馬國明放假一天"},{"pid":"5c92da364410206ff07577ef4a1688194d8b1d53","tid":1112660,"uid":92465,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T14:01:46.000Z","msg":"聲明的確表現馬國明氣度，我亦唔排除他真係一個好男人。但他始終係公眾人物，言行聲明會失去好多自主性。人性是有多面體而複雜，我傾向持有保留態度，不會現刻說什麼好男人或定下過早結論。"},{"pid":"50c67013c7772ce22d0a05ae80b25f0632830178","tid":1112660,"uid":92465,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T14:02:21.000Z","msg":"馬明未經歷過實戰喎，佢做左人老公，生埋仔，養大埋先好講。話個婚姻係童話係咒佢兩公婆。話人好男人/好女人，當事人聽左入去飄飄然就易衰啲道理一樣。<br />\n自由既代價係恆常警惕政府，咁婚姻美滿既代價就係兩公婆時常留意同異性保持距離。講真，咩好男人，好女人呢d評價，要當事人死左先係時候講。<br />\n婚姻冇咩童話，甘心平淡過日子最唔易出事，想刺激，想要童話，下個出事既就係自己。"},{"pid":"8285407f035f253584c2187f55d5dcad5ee8b8ea","tid":1112660,"uid":92465,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T14:03:04.000Z","msg":"馬明無疑回應得體，表現大方氣度，我欣賞他。但我不禁問，這是否證明他就是一名好伴侶呢？<br />\n<br />\n應該傷心時不去傷心，凡事看開，只顧為人設想，這樣不愠不火的男子，是否就適合成為戀人，值得想一想。"},{"pid":"2fcd7b85013c77f665d28e532496c882da913d32","tid":1112660,"uid":5995,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T14:03:46.000Z","msg":"廢柴 唔識發嬲<br />\n比人恰到上心口"},{"pid":"4db3edea2ee6c6eb6971a758b4dc79dc45d13cfe","tid":1112660,"uid":13448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f0c306b32b3f4b180fa806e64aaed2f3fe4b7e71","tid":1112660,"uid":88491,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"08bb73cb62f16a1b2f592a28efdba7018054eedd","tid":1112660,"uid":112211,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"98231165ebaad883bced72954753680230139fcf","tid":1112660,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T13:36:23.000Z","msg":"馬國明係一個好好嘅人"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T13:37:13.000Z","msg":"馬明係一個冇壞既人"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T13:38:25.000Z","msg":"馬明係一個有靈魂嘅人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T14:05:04.000Z","msg":"笑左出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"821923163681b189fc5e8f0a13fe45e9d38e858f","tid":1112660,"uid":4917,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T14:09:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/29omCcQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F29omCcQ.png&h=aa1e01c4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"38f1fcb016f7a177ac686d5c9abfd6d2f8dfc6df","tid":1112660,"uid":82169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f0c306b32b3f4b180fa806e64aaed2f3fe4b7e71","tid":1112660,"uid":88491,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"08bb73cb62f16a1b2f592a28efdba7018054eedd","tid":1112660,"uid":112211,"like":13,"dislike":